## Useful Props

* `pagingEnabled` – when true, the scroll view stops on multiples of its own size (like a pager).
* `showsVerticalScrollIndicator` / `showsHorizontalScrollIndicator` – toggle scroll bars.
* `onScroll` – event fired while scrolling (use with `scrollEventThrottle`).
* `contentContainerStyle` – styles applied to the inner container (useful for padding).

Example with onScroll:
```jsx
<ScrollView
  onScroll={(event) => {
    console.log(event.nativeEvent.contentOffset.y);
  }}
  scrollEventThrottle={16}
>
  ...
</ScrollView>
```

